name: Testing Strategy
description: Guidelines for writing and organizing tests.

---

Frontend:
- Unit Testing: React Testing Library
- Coverage Tool: Vitest + coverage provider
- Mocking: MSW (for API mocking)
- Linting: ESLint + TypeScript strict mode

Backend:
- Unit Testing: pytest
- Validation Testing: Pydantic schema unit tests
- API Testing: HTTPX + pytest fixtures
- Mocks: Use unittest.mock or pytest-mock for external APIs

Coverage Goals:
- Minimum: 70% (core modules)
- Target: 90%+ (for all new features)
